title: Amiga music: Virgill - The Nature of Magic demo OST (A1200🎧Dolbyfied)
description:
Soundtrack from "The Nature of Magic" demo (New Generation Crew) by Virgill/Alcatraz^Haujobb^MoS. Demo ranked 6th at Revision 2023.
Art from the demo by Erk/Facet/Made/Prowler, don't know who made what.

Demo can be watched here:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x4yjY6FRBv4

Made using real A1200 Rev. 1D.4 audio.

Visit my channel for more Amiga music.
